made it into the marketplace.

00:21:53.750 --> 00:21:56.170 align:middle line:10%
So what happened was,
through some lobbying efforts

00:21:56.170 --> 00:21:58.770 align:middle line:10%
and in the Telecommunication
Act when it was finally passed,

00:21:58.770 --> 00:22:02.890 align:middle line:10%
the EPA's RF program
